    <div class="field field-name-field-images field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/content/state-rest-headless-drupal-8"><img src="http://build2be.com/sites/build2be.com/files/styles/medium/public/d8rest.png?itok=ger92Z5v" width="220" height="220" alt="Drupal 8 ReST" title="Drupal 8 ReST" /></a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>One of the Drupal 8 initiatives was to make "headless" Drupal core work out of the box. Drupal now has a ReST API.</p>

<p>This allows you to use all the Drupal 8 features to edit your content but present the content not only on a Drupal frontend but also on mobile apps or anything else that can work with JSON data.</p>
